## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for language.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers source-language display,
translated/interpreted display,
bounded wording changes,
historical wording reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- language context must resolve
- source meaning basis must resolve
- translation/interpretation scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid language context
- invalid source meaning basis
- invalid translation scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish source wording,
translated/interpreted wording,
historical wording reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- language runtime scope is explicit
- source/translated rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
